  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA83">
<l>miṉpōluñ ceñcaṭaiyāṉ mālōṭu mīṇṭicaintā</l>
<l>leṉpōluṅ kāṇpārkaṭ keṉṟirē - ṟaṉpōlum</l>
<l>poṟkuṉṟu nīla maṇikkuṉṟun tāmuṭaṉē</l>
<l>niṟkiṉṟa pōlu neṭitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the one with the lightning-like red matted hair agrees to be in close contact with Māl,</l>
<l>what will it resemble for the onlookers? If you(pl.) speak [thus],</l>
<l>the long thing that stands there will resemble a golden mountain together</l>
<l>with a blue sapphire mountain, who resemble him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
